er-4 governed AI delivery.","Promote Daypaio greenfield architecture and event-storming evidence into the visible supporting-role set.","Compress narrow retrieval/tool keywords and foreground governance, reliability, stakeholder translation, and production delivery vocabulary.","Keep privacy/compliance references narrow and evidenced; avoid turning them into broad governance-program claims."],"citations":["data/master-cv/role_metadata.json:3","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:233","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:27","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:10"]},"curation_priorities":[{"priority_rank":1,"action":"Promote current-role architect-title provenance from knowledge-base into canonical role metadata.","why_now":"This is the cleanest way to support an architecture-first title family without fabricating a new title, and it directly improves headline safety for this category.","target_files":["data/master-cv/role_metadata.json","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md"],"source_refs":["docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:7","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:98","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:181","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:268","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:360"],"expected_category_impact":"High: strengthens safe use of architect-focused positioning and reduces reliance on generic leadership framing.","citation":"Not yet curated from multiple upstream STAR records that consistently describe the current role with technical-architect wording."},{"priority_rank":2,"action":"Promote Daypaio greenfield architecture, event-storming, and launch narrative into a stronger architect-facing evidence 