slation together; the evidence exists but is not surfaced together."},{"priority_rank":3,"action":"Reorder Seven.One bullets so AI platform engineering, north-star architecture, observability, and CI/CD sit above narrower people/hiring bullets.","section":"role_bullets","why_now":"The category prefers architecture, delivery, governance, and reliability over hiring or team-building emphasis.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:71","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:233","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:332"],"citation":"This improves alignment with category signals that overweight architecture, delivery, governance, and stakeholder communication rather than formal management."},{"priority_rank":4,"action":"Refactor project descriptions so Commander-4 and Lantern read as architecture/governance/reliability proofs, not mainly retrieval-tool inventories.","section":"projects","why_now":"The current project representation is technically impressive but too implementation-granular for this target category.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:10"],"citation":"The category values governed delivery, evaluation, reliability, and cost-aware decisions more than raw tool detail."},{"priority_rank":5,"action":"Rebuild the skills priority block around architecture, governance, delivery, reliability, and stakeholder vocabulary, with vendor/tool names secondary.","section":"skills","why_now":"The current skills list is crowded with narrow technical terms and does not read as architecture-first.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:10","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:233"],"citation":"This category has no single dominant keyword; validated architecture outcomes should lead over keyword stuffing."},{"priority_rank":6,"action":"Bring Daypaio’s greenfield platform and event-storming work into the visible supporting-role narrative.","section":"role_bullets","why_now":"It closes the only major scope imbalance in the current representation: strong brownfield, weaker visible greenfield.","supported_by":["data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:27","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:142"],"citation":"Greenfield proof is already curated and should be surfaced because the category repeatedly values both greenfield and brownfield scope."}],"evidence_ledger":[{"recommendation":"Anchor the category narrative in enterprise platform architecture and modernization outcomes.","classification":"supported_and_curated","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:28","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:54","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:71"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Use governed AI workflow delivery as the main AI-specific differentiator.","classification":"supported_and_curated","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:282","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:332","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Present leadership as player-coach technical direction, not as executive people management.","classification":"supported_and_curated","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:88","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:182"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Elevate Daypaio greenfield architecture to complement Seven.One brownfield transformation.","classification":"curated_but_underrepresented","support":["data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:27","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:44","data/master-cv/roles/02_samdock_daypaio.md:142"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Promote current-role technical-architect wording into canonical metadata before using stronger architect title families downstream.","classification":"supported_upstream_pending_curation","support":["docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:7","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:98","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:181","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:268","docs/archive/knowledge-base.md:360"],"confidence":"high"},{"recommendation":"Surface stakeholder translation and risk communication more aggressively in the master CV.","classification":"curated_but_underrepresented","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:123","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:250","data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:266","data/master-cv/roles/06_clary_icon.md:103"],"confidence":"medium"},{"recommendation":"Use privacy/compliance experience only as narrow delivery proof, not as broad regulatory-program ownership.","classification":"curated_but_underrepresented","support":["data/master-cv/roles/01_seven_one_entertainment.md:106","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:8","data/master-cv/projects/commander4.md:9"],"confidence":"medium"},{"recommendation":"Avoid executive, deep multi-cloud, fine-tuning, RLHF, and prompt-specialist claims.","classification":"unsupported_or_unsafe","support":["data/master-cv/role_metadata.json:3","data/master-cv/projects/commander4_skills.json:42","data/master-cv/projects/lantern_skills.json:49","data/master-cv/projects/lantern.md:7"],"confidence":"high"}] }
